6: // Usage:
7: //   node score-candidate.cjs --candidate=<path> [--baseline=<path>] [--output=<path>]
8: //
9: // When --baseline is present, the scorer evaluates both files and emits:
10: //   baselineScore: weighted baseline score
11: //   delta: total and per-dimension candidate-minus-baseline score deltas
12: //   thresholdDelta: comparison threshold from --thresholdDelta, manifest scoring,
